[SHORT DESC]
Reduces Defense EVs by 10. Increases happiness.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>When used, it decreases one Pokemon's Defense EVs by 10 while raising happiness. Provides a one-time 70 power Poison attack when a Pokemon holding this item uses Natural Gift, and can be blended to make a Poffin with Sour, Spicy, and Sweet flavors.</p>